                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.3393/1–2549: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul at Tsingtao</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Strong</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-01-26T21:00:00-05:00"
                            >January 26, 1949—9 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>42. Dept understands (Contel 44 Jan 24[<hi rend="italic">25</hi>]) Navy has
                    forwarded Adm Badger material for use in connection any publicity re
                    withdrawal.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
